For all of you who dont know how to burn, or get subtitles, i've made a "guide"



First, download IMGburner, a program with good quality to burn img-files.

When you have downloaded this torrent, unrar all the files with winRAR.

When all files are unpacked, they should create a img. file....

Double-click the img.file, and if you have IMG-burner, then it should start to burn.

When it done burning, just start the disc, and if there is no menu in beginning, you should be able to find a menu in your DVD-player, or DVD-program at your computer, and just choose the subtitle you want. PM me if there is something you don't understand, and I'll try to explain better ;) Good Luck and enjoy the movie :)
